title: Biotech Comix
description:
Do you like obscure underground comics? Check out this Biotech Comix

This book was published by H.T. Philbrick and Associates in 1982 and has NO artist credited! 

The entire content seems to be by the same artist though, and it's a kinda cool style that looks a bit like Roberta Gregory (but i don't think it's her)

With cover colered in crayons

A sequel is announced on the back-cover but i have found no hard evidence of that ever bein published
